=Categorize this email:

***
**From:** {{ $json.from.value[0].address }}
**Subject:** {{ $json.subject }}
**Content:** 
{{ $json.text }}

**Attachment Data**
{{ $json.attachmentText.map((text, i) => `*Attachment ${i}:* \n${text}\n`).join('\n') }}
***

Please analyze this email and determine the appropriate category using the available data given to you.

parameters.jsCode:
// Group attachment texts by message_id
const groupedData = {};

for (const item of $input.all()) {
  const messageId = item.json.message_id;
  const text = item.json.text;

  if (!groupedData[messageId]) {
    groupedData[messageId] = {
      message_id: messageId,
      attachmentText: []
    };
  }

  groupedData[messageId].attachmentText.push(text);
}

// Convert to array of items
return Object.values(groupedData).map(data => ({
  json: data
}));
